Burn After Reading;;65;;78;;R;;When a disc containing memoirs of a former CIA analyst (John Malkovich) falls into the hands of Linda Litzke (Frances McDormand) and Chad Feldheimer (Brad Pitt), the two gym employees see a chance to make enough money for her to have life-changing cosmetic surgery. Predictably, events whirl out of control for the duo doofuses and those in their orbit.;;Drama,Comedy,Mystery & thriller;;Joel Coen,Ethan Coen;;2008;;George Clooney,Frances McDormand,John Malkovich,Tilda Swinton,Brad Pitt,Richard Jenkins,Elizabeth Marvel,David Rasche,J.K. Simmons,Jeffrey DeMunn,Olek Krupa,Michael Countryman;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/burn_after_reading